Optimum Coal Buys Two Prospecting Rights in South Africa For $63.4 Million

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-04T08:18:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-04/optimum-coal-buys-two-prospecting-rights-in-south-africa-for-63-4-million.html
Optimum Coal Holdings (OPT)  Ltd. said it has
acquired two prospecting rights close to Koornfontein Mines for
a cash consideration of 420 million rand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
